==In popular culture==
In the novel ''[[The Count of Monte Cristo]]'' by [[Alexandre Dumas]], the Teatro Argentina was the setting for an important scene during a performance of ''[[Parisina (opera)|Parisina]]'' by [[Gaetano Donizetti]].

